posts.post_title: WTB - N48 Dixie/Virginia Brights and N508 Sub Rosa
posts.post_content:
Looking for some type examples of these women ballplayer cards.  Raw or graded.  Low condition is fine but without major creases.  Might also consider a N508 complete set if there are any out there.  N48s must have good picture quality.

Thanks!
